// /get-started, with current-plan grey-out + downgrade confirmation modal).
// Visible when user has an active Stripe subscription. Reads the 6 non-trial
// Payment Link formula URLs + users.Plan (Ux1pf, LINKED_RECORD → pricing) so
// we can identify the user's current plan and grey it out. Click a card →
// selected. Click sticky CTA → if upgrade or interval-switch, navigate to
// the matching non-trial Payment Link directly. If the selected plan is a
// LOWER rank than current, show a confirm modal first listing what they
// lose (hours saved/month delta, max videos delta, workspaces, seats).

